{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make a mandatory \u2018no ai\u2019 logo for products and companies",
        "additional_details": "Furthermore, I have seen an example of this working. One creator had put a no ai logo on their product and majority of the feedback was people saying they would be more encouraged to buy the product despite them not having any real interest in it. This \u2018no ai\u2019 logo would bring back life to packing and designing and would make \u2018art\u2019, art again.",
        "background": "The use of ai has become widespread and more often than not, people will accidentally buy a product which uses ai as it can be hard to spot. By introducing this, people would be more encouraged to buy products and it would help people of all walks of life detect ai much more efficiently.",
